---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="MNL Innovation - Cloud Solutions"
	keywords="	Cloud Solutions, Cloud Services, Cloud Migration, Cloud Infrastructure, Cloud Security, Cloud Backup, Cloud Disaster Recovery, Cloud Cost Optimization"
	description=" MNL Innovation - Cloud Solutions"
>
	<div class="bg-white mt-20">
		<main
			class="mx-auto px-4 pb-24 pt-14 sm:px-6 sm:pb-32 sm:pt-16 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8"
		>
			<!-- Product -->
			<div
				class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-7 lg:grid-rows-1 lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-10 xl:gap-x-16"
			>
				<!-- Product image -->
				<div class="lg:col-span-4 lg:row-end-1">
					<div
						class="aspect-h-3 aspect-w-4 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
					>
						<img
							src="/images/services/cloud.jpg"
							alt="MNL Innovation Cloud Solutions "
							class="object-cover object-center bg-repeat"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Product details -->
				<div
					class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-2xl sm:mt-16 lg:col-span-3 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-end-2 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none"
				>
					<div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
						<div class="mt-4">
							<h1
								class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-3xl"
							>
								What Are Cloud Solutions?
							</h1>

							<h2 id="information-heading" class="sr-only">
								What Are Cloud Solutions?
							</h2>
						</div>
					</div>

					<p class="mt-6 text-gray-500">
						Cloud solutions refer to the delivery of computing services—such as
						storage, servers, databases, networking, software, and
						analytics—over the internet ("the cloud"). These services provide
						flexible resources, faster innovation, and economies of scale.
						Whether you're looking to migrate your infrastructure, enhance
						collaboration, or scale your apps globally, cloud solutions empower
						your business to work smarter and more efficiently.
					</p>

					<div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-6 gap-y-4 sm:grid-cols-1">
						<a
							href="/contact?service=cloud"
							class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border bg-[#00629E] px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white hover:bg-[#00629E] hover:text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2"
						>
							Contact
						</a>
					</div>

					<!-- Lista de servicios -->
					<div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900">
							Key Features of Our Cloud Solutions
						</h3>
						<div class="prose prose-sm mt-4 text-gray-500">
							<ul role="list" class="space-y-6">
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Scalability:</strong> Instantly scale resources up
											or down based on demand.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Cost Efficiency:</strong> Pay only for what you use, with reduced upfront infrastructure costs.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Remote Accessibility:</strong> Access your systems and data securely from anywhere in the world.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Business Continuity:</strong> Built-in backup, failover, and disaster recovery options.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>High Availability:</strong>Infrastructure designed for uptime and reliability.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Security & Compliance:</strong> Data encryption, identity access management, and compliance with industry standards.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div
					class="mx-auto mt-16 w-full max-w-2xl lg:col-span-4 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none"
				>
					<div>
						<div class="border-b border-gray-200">
							<h3
								class="text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-800 text-xl font-medium border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-[#1dc690] py-6"
							>
              What’s Included in Our Cloud Services
							</h3>
						</div>

						<div
							id="tab-panel-faq"
							class="text-sm text-gray-500"
							aria-labelledby="tab-faq"
							role="tabpanel"
							tabindex="0"
						>
							<h3 class="sr-only">
								What’s Included in Our Cloud Service
							</h3>

							<dl>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
                  <strong>Cloud Migration:</strong> Seamless transition from on-premise to cloud infrastructure.
								</dt>

								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									<strong>Cloud Infrastructure Setup:</strong> Provisioning of virtual machines, databases, and networking.
								</dt>

								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									<strong>SaaS, PaaS, IaaS Consulting:</strong> Strategic guidance on Software, Platform, and Infrastructure as a Service.
								</dt>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									<strong>Hybrid & Multi-Cloud Support:</strong> Integration of cloud services with existing on-premise systems.
								</dt>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									<strong>Backup & Disaster Recovery Solutions:</strong> Robust, automated backup and business continuity planning.
								</dt>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									<strong>Cloud Cost Optimization:</strong> Regular audits and cost-saving recommendations.
								</dt>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									<strong>Identity & Access Management:</strong> Role-based access control and secure login practices (e.g., MFA).
								</dt>							
							</dl>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
						<div class="border-b border-gray-200">
							<h3
								class="text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-800 text-xl font-medium border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-[#1dc690] py-6"
							>
              Technologies & Platforms We Use
							</h3>
						</div>

						<div
							id="tab-panel-faq"
							class="text-sm text-gray-500"
							aria-labelledby="tab-faq"
							role="tabpanel"
							tabindex="0"
						>
							<h3 class="sr-only">Technologies & Platforms We Use</h3>

							<dl>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									<strong>Microsoft Azure:</strong> Infrastructure, AI services, virtual desktops, and more for enterprise-grade applications.
								</dt>
							</dl>

							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong>Microsoft 365 / Google Workspace:</strong> Cloud productivity platforms for email, collaboration, and storage.
							</dt>

							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong>VMware Cloud:</strong> Hybrid cloud infrastructure with seamless integration between on-prem and cloud environments.
							</dt>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong>Cloudflare & Vercel:</strong> Edge deployment, CDN, and performance enhancements for web applications.
							</dt>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong>Amazon Web Services (AWS):</strong> Full suite of cloud services including EC2, S3, Lambda, RDS, and CloudFront.
							</dt>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong>Google Cloud Platform (GCP):</strong> Containerized apps, analytics, and AI-powered solutions.
							</dt>
							
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div
				class="mx-auto mt-16 w-full max-w-2xl lg:col-span-4 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none"
			>
				<div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
					<div class="border-b border-gray-200">
						<h3
							class="text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-800 text-xl font-medium border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-[#1dc690] py-6"
						>
							Frequently Asked Questions
						</h3>
					</div>

					<div
						id="tab-panel-faq"
						class="text-sm text-gray-500"
						aria-labelledby="tab-faq"
						role="tabpanel"
						tabindex="0"
					>
						<h3 class="sr-only">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

						<dl>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q1:  What are the benefits of moving to the cloud?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: Cloud computing reduces hardware costs, improves scalability, enhances security, and provides the flexibility to work from anywhere.
								</p>
							</dd>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q2: How secure are cloud solutions?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: We implement enterprise-grade security protocols including data encryption, firewalls, MFA, and compliance monitoring to protect your assets.
								</p>
							</dd>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q3: Will I lose control over my systems in the cloud?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: Not at all. You retain full control over your data and systems while benefiting from automation, scalability, and remote access.
								</p>
							</dd>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q4: Can you migrate our existing apps and data to the cloud?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: Yes. We specialize in seamless cloud migrations with minimal downtime and data integrity protection.
								</p>
							</dd>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q5:  What if we need a hybrid approach?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: No problem. We support hybrid cloud environments that combine on-premise infrastructure with cloud services for maximum flexibility.
								</p>
							</dd>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q6:  How do you help manage cloud costs?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: We perform regular audits, identify underutilized resources, and implement automation to help you optimize spending.
								</p>
							</dd>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q7:  Is training included for our team?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: Yes, we offer user onboarding and admin training as part of our service to ensure your team is confident using the cloud.
								</p>
							</dd>
						</dl>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
	</div>
</Layout>
